1
00:00:06,045 --> 00:00:10,848
(2003,
two years before An Ruoxi's murder)

2
00:00:19,936 --> 00:00:20,735
Mr. Tu.

3
00:00:22,096 --> 00:00:23,256
Take a look.

4
00:00:24,215 --> 00:00:25,215
Just this single page

5
00:00:25,976 --> 00:00:28,215
shows over 30 million dollars
in transactions.

6
00:00:29,096 --> 00:00:30,896
If I hadn't found this ledger,

7
00:00:32,175 --> 00:00:34,096
were you planning
to keep these shady things

8
00:00:34,655 --> 00:00:36,495
from me forever?

9
00:00:38,896 --> 00:00:39,775
Ruoxi.

10
00:00:40,496 --> 00:00:41,536
Some things

11
00:00:42,256 --> 00:00:43,695
are better left unknown to you.

12
00:00:46,455 --> 00:00:47,335
Right.

13
00:00:48,976 --> 00:00:50,695
I'd better know nothing at all.

14
00:00:52,695 --> 00:00:54,415
I'd better not be your woman.

15
00:00:56,015 --> 00:00:57,536
I'd better remain

16
00:00:58,055 --> 00:00:59,415
the hostess who came

17
00:01:00,415 --> 00:01:03,015
to Deep In The Bustle
just to make a living.

18
00:01:04,695 --> 00:01:06,455
I'd better have never dreamed

19
00:01:07,415 --> 00:01:09,735
of living an ordinary life with you.

20
00:01:12,295 --> 00:01:13,096
What a pity.

21
00:01:14,775 --> 00:01:16,575
All that is just a fantasy.

22
00:01:18,295 --> 00:01:19,816
I'm already in the game.

23
00:01:20,495 --> 00:01:21,495
Tell me,

24
00:01:21,495 --> 00:01:22,695
how can I...

25
00:01:30,472 --> 00:01:32,896
=The Glory Fades=

26
00:01:33,397 --> 00:01:35,808
=Episode 3=
(In the Game)

27
00:01:35,808 --> 00:01:36,415
(2005, four hours
after An Ruoxi's death)

28
00:01:36,415 --> 00:01:37,016
Who died?

29
00:01:37,016 --> 00:01:37,816
What happened?

30
00:01:37,855 --> 00:01:38,656
It's An Ruoxi.

31
00:01:39,376 --> 00:01:40,832
I heard it was

32
00:01:40,832 --> 00:01:42,656
An Ruoxi, Deep In The Bustle's
top courtesan.

33
00:01:42,656 --> 00:01:43,575
Clearly dirty cops.

34
00:01:43,575 --> 00:01:45,824
She made tons of money

35
00:01:45,824 --> 00:01:47,135
following Tu Jiasheng.

36
00:01:47,736 --> 00:01:49,616
Earned it, never got to spend it.

37
00:01:54,442 --> 00:01:56,960
(Du Hansi, Captain of Criminal
Investigation, Changqingtai Police)

38
00:02:11,295 --> 00:02:12,736
Mr. He.

39
00:02:12,976 --> 00:02:15,415
May I call you brother?

40
00:02:16,656 --> 00:02:19,615
I always wished I had one
since I was little.

41
00:02:19,776 --> 00:02:21,376
That way when people bully me,

42
00:02:21,415 --> 00:02:23,175
I wouldn't be so scared.

43
00:02:23,816 --> 00:02:24,776
If I could have

44
00:02:24,776 --> 00:02:26,735
a brother as powerful

45
00:02:26,735 --> 00:02:28,256
and handsome as you,

46
00:02:28,895 --> 00:02:30,895
I'd be happy.

47
00:02:31,936 --> 00:02:33,695
That's easily done.

48
00:02:33,936 --> 00:02:36,496
From now on, you're my sister.

49
00:02:37,415 --> 00:02:38,976
Brother.

50
00:02:39,256 --> 00:02:40,936
Brother, let me toast you.

51
00:02:40,936 --> 00:02:41,656
Okay.

52
00:02:45,575 --> 00:02:46,496
Bottoms up.

53
00:02:48,936 --> 00:02:49,735
Good drinker.

54
00:02:59,735 --> 00:03:00,656
Mr. Tu.

55
00:03:05,536 --> 00:03:06,415
Mr. Tu.

56
00:03:09,015 --> 00:03:11,615
Mr. Tu, let me toast you.

57
00:03:12,056 --> 00:03:13,895
Since I came to Deep In The Bustle,

58
00:03:14,455 --> 00:03:15,855
thanks to you,

59
00:03:15,855 --> 00:03:17,295
I've come this far.

60
00:03:18,455 --> 00:03:19,216
Enough.

61
00:03:19,656 --> 00:03:20,615
You girls,

62
00:03:20,615 --> 00:03:22,615
go enjoy yourselves in the next room
with Boris.

63
00:03:22,776 --> 00:03:23,776
We need to talk.

64
00:04:14,695 --> 00:04:15,656
Mr. He.

65
00:04:17,295 --> 00:04:19,216
Can we talk

66
00:04:19,776 --> 00:04:21,336
about the project now?

67
00:04:25,016 --> 00:04:25,896
Mr. Tu.

68
00:04:27,615 --> 00:04:28,696
Ocean-Three project

69
00:04:28,696 --> 00:04:30,175
is a national key project.

70
00:04:30,896 --> 00:04:33,615
The Cabinet and the capital
are watching closely.

71
00:04:34,055 --> 00:04:34,776
As it stands,

72
00:04:35,495 --> 00:04:37,656
we've received over 2,000 bid proposals.

73
00:04:37,656 --> 00:04:39,896
Eighteen of those are main bids.

74
00:04:40,935 --> 00:04:42,615
None short on money

75
00:04:42,615 --> 00:04:44,295
or qualifications.

76
00:04:46,216 --> 00:04:47,976
Jackson from your city

77
00:04:48,175 --> 00:04:49,855
is being transferred back to county HQ.

78
00:04:50,456 --> 00:04:51,336
Do you know it?

79
00:04:55,456 --> 00:04:57,055
I think the replacement

80
00:04:57,055 --> 00:04:59,136
should be promoted

81
00:04:59,136 --> 00:05:00,136
from deputy mayors.

82
00:05:00,976 --> 00:05:02,495
No parachuting in.

83
00:05:18,016 --> 00:05:20,216
People need to aim high.

84
00:05:21,216 --> 00:05:21,896
Right?

85
00:06:09,255 --> 00:06:12,216
Mr. Tu, I know you have connections.

86
00:06:12,375 --> 00:06:14,976
Deep In The Bustle

87
00:06:14,976 --> 00:06:17,456
is known as the underground
Personnel Bureau.

88
00:06:17,855 --> 00:06:20,255
But there's only one week left.

89
00:06:20,776 --> 00:06:21,656
I'm afraid

90
00:06:22,096 --> 00:06:25,656
the Bureau's evaluation discussions
have concluded.

91
00:06:27,456 --> 00:06:28,935
Do you know Mr. Zuo?

92
00:06:31,456 --> 00:06:32,295
Jiasheng.

93
00:06:32,935 --> 00:06:34,336
Of course.

94
00:06:34,656 --> 00:06:36,456
The director
of the Cabinet Personnel Bureau.

95
00:06:36,456 --> 00:06:37,855
Even an outsider like me knows him.

96
00:06:38,216 --> 00:06:39,735
Mr. He, you know him, right?

97
00:06:49,776 --> 00:06:51,136
So many higher-ups.

98
00:06:53,815 --> 00:06:55,336
Hello? Jiasheng?

99
00:06:56,255 --> 00:06:57,055
Zuo.

100
00:06:57,656 --> 00:06:59,855
Has the big list for next month
been finalized?

101
00:07:00,336 --> 00:07:01,656
It's basically settled.

102
00:07:01,656 --> 00:07:02,576
Just not announced.

103
00:07:02,896 --> 00:07:03,615
What's up?

104
00:07:03,935 --> 00:07:06,615
After Jackson's transfer,
is there a replacement?

105
00:07:07,976 --> 00:07:09,935
Jiasheng, come on, be direct.

106
00:07:10,136 --> 00:07:10,976
What's it about?

107
00:07:11,776 --> 00:07:12,615
He Mike.

108
00:07:14,055 --> 00:07:15,375
He was discussed,

109
00:07:15,375 --> 00:07:16,735
but passed over.

110
00:07:17,255 --> 00:07:18,656
Can he be put back on the list?

111
00:07:18,896 --> 00:07:20,935
Jiasheng, that depends on the Cabinet.

112
00:07:21,375 --> 00:07:23,735
Both Nie Feng's father
and the Grand Princess

113
00:07:24,255 --> 00:07:25,656
have a say.

114
00:07:26,415 --> 00:07:28,336
I'll handle the Cabinet.

115
00:07:28,696 --> 00:07:29,536
Jiasheng.

116
00:07:29,536 --> 00:07:30,776
Seems you and Deputy Mayor He

117
00:07:30,776 --> 00:07:32,136
have a special relationship.

118
00:07:32,136 --> 00:07:32,935
Right.

119
00:07:33,656 --> 00:07:34,735
We are friends.

120
00:07:35,735 --> 00:07:36,415
Right?

121
00:07:53,255 --> 00:07:55,656
Mr. He, your matter is settled.

122
00:07:55,976 --> 00:07:58,216
Now it's time for mine, right?

123
00:08:27,776 --> 00:08:28,536
Du Hansi.

124
00:08:28,776 --> 00:08:29,375
Yes.

125
00:08:29,696 --> 00:08:31,656
Withdraw

126
00:08:31,656 --> 00:08:32,855
from An Ruoxi's crime scene.

127
00:08:33,096 --> 00:08:33,935
But...

128
00:08:33,935 --> 00:08:34,935
- I-I've...
- But what?

129
00:08:34,935 --> 00:08:35,735
Do you not get it?

130
00:08:35,735 --> 00:08:37,096
This is Deputy Mayor He's order.

131
00:08:37,216 --> 00:08:38,735
He just called. Withdraw.

132
00:08:38,735 --> 00:08:39,456
Got it.

133
00:08:39,456 --> 00:08:40,375
Handle the scene.

134
00:08:40,576 --> 00:08:41,416
I will...

135
00:08:41,576 --> 00:08:42,535
I'll handle it.

136
00:08:43,255 --> 00:08:43,816
Understood.

137
00:08:43,816 --> 00:08:44,416
You take care.

138
00:08:44,816 --> 00:08:45,615
Alright.

139
00:08:54,656 --> 00:08:56,928
(Six months later)

140
00:08:57,375 --> 00:08:58,176
(Six months ago,)

141
00:08:58,176 --> 00:08:59,655
(An Ruoxi was found dead)

142
00:08:59,655 --> 00:09:00,976
(at the West Suburb villa.)

143
00:09:00,976 --> 00:09:02,576
(The specific cause of her murder)

144
00:09:02,576 --> 00:09:05,296
(The Police Issued Statement)
(has drawn widespread public attention.)

145
00:09:05,495 --> 00:09:06,135
(on An Ruoxi Case)
(Regarding this,)

146
00:09:06,135 --> 00:09:08,176
(Chief Zheng Xili)

147
00:09:08,176 --> 00:09:09,456
(stated as follows.)

148
00:09:09,456 --> 00:09:10,135
(Zheng Xili, Police Chief)
(We)

149
00:09:10,135 --> 00:09:11,576
(have made big breakthroughs.)

150
00:09:12,096 --> 00:09:13,015
(The suspect)

151
00:09:13,015 --> 00:09:15,936
(is very likely
a mentally ill individual)

152
00:09:16,456 --> 00:09:18,375
(who had never met the victim.)

153
00:09:18,375 --> 00:09:19,176
(We assure everyone)

154
00:09:19,456 --> 00:09:21,696
(that we will give you)

155
00:09:21,696 --> 00:09:22,855
(a satisfactory answer.)

156
00:09:23,176 --> 00:09:23,775
(Furthermore,)

157
00:09:23,775 --> 00:09:24,816
(Chief Zheng pointed out)

158
00:09:24,816 --> 00:09:26,615
(that police have narrowed down)

159
00:09:26,615 --> 00:09:28,176
(several possible suspects.)

160
00:09:28,176 --> 00:09:30,735
(The capture of the killer is imminent.)

161
00:09:30,855 --> 00:09:31,655
Tu Jiasheng.

162
00:09:32,615 --> 00:09:34,015
The police may be incompetent.

163
00:09:35,015 --> 00:09:35,816
Are you?

164
00:09:39,056 --> 00:09:40,615
Hello, is this Ms. Su?

165
00:09:40,615 --> 00:09:42,944
We see you've signed up
for Wine Appreciation,

166
00:09:42,944 --> 00:09:44,544
Luxury Goods and Jewelry Recognition,

167
00:09:44,544 --> 00:09:45,952
Equestrian, and other courses.

168
00:09:46,432 --> 00:09:47,776
We want to confirm with you.

169
00:09:47,776 --> 00:09:49,096
Was this a mistake or...

170
00:09:49,096 --> 00:09:49,632
No.

171
00:09:50,336 --> 00:09:51,255
It's not a mistake.

172
00:09:51,976 --> 00:09:52,816
I'll take them all.

173
00:09:53,735 --> 00:09:56,096
(I can't accept
the police's conclusion.)

174
00:09:56,456 --> 00:09:58,056
(I must enter Deep In The Bustle)

175
00:09:58,456 --> 00:10:00,336
(to find the real killer of Ruoxi.)

176
00:10:00,976 --> 00:10:01,816
(Jewelry Appraisal)
(I know)

177
00:10:02,216 --> 00:10:04,416
(entering Deep In The Bustle
is dangerous.)

178
00:10:04,416 --> 00:10:04,936
(Wine Appreciation)

179
00:10:04,936 --> 00:10:06,216
(But I have no choice.)

180
00:10:06,775 --> 00:10:08,216
(Cigar Tasting)
(All I can do)

181
00:10:08,216 --> 00:10:09,456
(Taekwondo)
(is learning more skills)

182
00:10:09,576 --> 00:10:10,735
(and arming myself)

183
00:10:10,895 --> 00:10:13,895
(Swimming, Driving Skills)
(to get ready for this battle.)

184
00:10:15,136 --> 00:10:19,392
(2006, one year after An Ruoxi's death)

185
00:10:22,255 --> 00:10:24,895
From now on, listen to Yunyan.

186
00:10:25,336 --> 00:10:27,456
That's it for today's training.

187
00:10:27,735 --> 00:10:28,615
Dismissed.

188
00:10:31,976 --> 00:10:33,296
Are you blind?

189
00:10:33,696 --> 00:10:34,775
Do you take me for nothing?

190
00:10:34,775 --> 00:10:35,775
I'm sorry, Yunyan.

191
00:10:35,775 --> 00:10:37,056
Do you think I'm just air?

192
00:10:37,056 --> 00:10:38,096
Am I that unnoticeable?

193
00:10:38,696 --> 00:10:39,855
I didn't see you.

194
00:10:39,855 --> 00:10:41,735
- This is international brand!
- Sorry.

195
00:10:41,855 --> 00:10:43,296
Even if you work for ten years,

196
00:10:43,296 --> 00:10:44,296
you couldn't afford it!

197
00:10:44,456 --> 00:10:46,255
I didn't mean to.

198
00:10:47,096 --> 00:10:48,615
Clean it off right now!

199
00:10:49,096 --> 00:10:49,816
Crying?

200
00:10:49,816 --> 00:10:51,096
All you do is cry.

201
00:10:51,096 --> 00:10:52,456
Does crying solve anything?

202
00:10:53,255 --> 00:10:54,216
What I just said?

203
00:10:54,216 --> 00:10:55,176
You've forgotten?

204
00:10:57,015 --> 00:10:58,696
- Su Yunian, don't go.
- Take me for nothing?

205
00:10:58,696 --> 00:11:00,535
- Yunyan's a veteran here.
- Am I that invisible?

206
00:11:00,535 --> 00:11:02,416
- She might even become Mr. Tu's wife.
- Sorry.

207
00:11:02,416 --> 00:11:03,735
- I didn't mean to.
- We can't offend her.

208
00:11:03,936 --> 00:11:05,696
- Sorry?
- Mr. Tu's wife?

209
00:11:05,816 --> 00:11:07,096
I've told you many times.

210
00:11:07,096 --> 00:11:09,255
- Then she's worth offending.
- No manners at all.

211
00:11:09,255 --> 00:11:10,416
Do you even want this job?

212
00:11:10,416 --> 00:11:11,176
You.

213
00:11:11,936 --> 00:11:13,976
Look at what you did!

214
00:11:14,296 --> 00:11:16,056
These are international brand.

215
00:11:26,495 --> 00:11:28,375
(These shoes are obviously fake.)

216
00:11:28,696 --> 00:11:30,696
(The color and texture are off.)

217
00:11:31,976 --> 00:11:33,535
(At best, they're grade-A fakes.)

218
00:11:35,816 --> 00:11:37,976
Even the color's off!

219
00:11:37,976 --> 00:11:39,296
I almost thought they were fakes.

220
00:11:41,615 --> 00:11:42,375
Yunyan.

221
00:11:42,375 --> 00:11:43,096
Don't spare her.

222
00:11:43,176 --> 00:11:44,655
Make her take these shoes tomorrow

223
00:11:44,655 --> 00:11:45,976
to the boutique for maintenance.

224
00:11:48,696 --> 00:11:49,495
Forget it.

225
00:11:49,775 --> 00:11:51,176
I'm not that mean.

226
00:11:52,895 --> 00:11:54,495
Apologize to Yunyan now!

227
00:11:54,696 --> 00:11:56,456
She's being generous.

228
00:11:57,416 --> 00:11:58,655
I'm sorry, Yunyan.

229
00:11:58,655 --> 00:12:00,456
I'll be more careful next time.

230
00:12:00,755 --> 00:12:01,255
No, no!

231
00:12:01,255 --> 00:12:02,416
I won't do it again.

232
00:12:04,176 --> 00:12:04,976
Yunyan.

233
00:12:04,976 --> 00:12:06,456
If there's nothing else,

234
00:12:06,456 --> 00:12:07,576
we'll take our leave.

235
00:12:08,895 --> 00:12:09,615
You.

236
00:12:09,615 --> 00:12:10,416
Stay.

237
00:12:15,816 --> 00:12:17,855
You're Su Yunian, right?

238
00:12:18,775 --> 00:12:19,375
Yes.

239
00:12:19,895 --> 00:12:21,015
What is it?

240
00:12:21,976 --> 00:12:25,855
Are you sure your surname is Su, not An?

241
00:12:29,296 --> 00:12:29,855
An?

242
00:12:31,255 --> 00:12:32,775
I don't understand.

243
00:12:36,176 --> 00:12:36,976
Nothing.

244
00:12:37,696 --> 00:12:39,816
You just look like someone I hate.

245
00:12:43,655 --> 00:12:45,895
That person is named An?

246
00:12:47,615 --> 00:12:49,296
Do we look that alike?

247
00:12:49,615 --> 00:12:50,816
Could I meet her?

248
00:12:55,096 --> 00:12:56,015
Meet?

249
00:12:56,816 --> 00:12:58,495
You won't be meeting her.

250
00:13:00,775 --> 00:13:02,096
But it's not entirely impossible.

251
00:13:02,976 --> 00:13:04,176
I'm warning you.

252
00:13:04,855 --> 00:13:07,416
Keep your head down here.

253
00:13:08,216 --> 00:13:09,495
Otherwise,

254
00:13:09,895 --> 00:13:12,336
I might just send you to meet her.

255
00:13:14,535 --> 00:13:15,936
Even your chest is the same flat.

256
00:13:16,416 --> 00:13:17,895
Who do you think you are?

257
00:13:17,895 --> 00:13:19,696
Yunyan, don't be mad.

258
00:13:20,696 --> 00:13:22,015
(Ruoxi's diary)

259
00:13:22,015 --> 00:13:23,895
(mentioned Yunyan's jealousy.)

260
00:13:24,255 --> 00:13:25,895
(I thought she was suspicious.)

261
00:13:26,216 --> 00:13:27,216
(But now it seems)

262
00:13:27,456 --> 00:13:28,976
(she's just brainless)

263
00:13:28,976 --> 00:13:30,255
(and shallow,)

264
00:13:30,456 --> 00:13:32,375
(even dreaming
of becoming Mr. Tu's wife.)

265
00:13:36,216 --> 00:13:36,816
Su Yunian.

266
00:13:40,096 --> 00:13:41,456
Mr. Chu?

267
00:13:42,015 --> 00:13:44,135
Why bring your old gear to work?

268
00:13:46,655 --> 00:13:47,895
(Chu Bai, part-time bartender)
Is this your new outfit?

269
00:13:48,096 --> 00:13:49,176
(of Deep In The Bustle)
I've never seen you wear it.

270
00:13:49,936 --> 00:13:51,176
Yes.

271
00:13:55,135 --> 00:13:57,375
Do you really work here now?

272
00:13:58,296 --> 00:14:00,296
From now on, we're colleagues.

273
00:14:02,855 --> 00:14:04,135
Do you know what place this is?

274
00:14:04,936 --> 00:14:05,855
Of course.

275
00:14:06,176 --> 00:14:07,535
I wouldn't be here otherwise.

276
00:14:09,056 --> 00:14:10,176
It is dangerous

277
00:14:10,456 --> 00:14:11,375
and dirty.

278
00:14:13,976 --> 00:14:14,576
Take it.

279
00:14:14,696 --> 00:14:15,456
It's hot.

280
00:14:16,855 --> 00:14:18,535
Like when you left the library.

281
00:14:18,535 --> 00:14:19,336
Go home.

282
00:14:19,495 --> 00:14:20,216
Okay?

283
00:14:22,176 --> 00:14:23,375
But you came too, didn't you?

284
00:14:23,775 --> 00:14:25,895
And you've worked here over half a year.

285
00:14:26,176 --> 00:14:27,855
I'm just a bartender.

286
00:14:27,976 --> 00:14:29,775
It's different for girls here.

287
00:14:30,096 --> 00:14:31,296
What's different?

288
00:14:31,855 --> 00:14:33,576
I'm just a waitress.

289
00:14:33,976 --> 00:14:35,735
Carrying trays and taking orders.

290
00:14:36,696 --> 00:14:38,456
Chu Bai, don't overthink it.

291
00:14:46,656 --> 00:14:48,704
(Zheng Xili, Chief
of Changqingtai Police Department)

292
00:14:49,176 --> 00:14:49,855
Chief Zheng.

293
00:14:50,416 --> 00:14:51,576
Deputy Mayor He is here.

294
00:14:52,456 --> 00:14:53,015
Mr. He?

295
00:14:53,015 --> 00:14:55,015
What brings you here?

296
00:14:56,296 --> 00:14:57,135
Chief Zheng.

297
00:14:57,615 --> 00:14:59,456
An Ruoxi's case

298
00:14:59,895 --> 00:15:00,735
ends here.

299
00:15:00,895 --> 00:15:01,895
Stop it.

300
00:15:03,336 --> 00:15:04,255
But,

301
00:15:04,816 --> 00:15:06,696
the public needs an explanation.

302
00:15:07,176 --> 00:15:08,775
The news and rumors

303
00:15:08,775 --> 00:15:10,176
are getting out of control.

304
00:15:10,176 --> 00:15:11,696
- I'm afraid...
- Chief Zheng.

305
00:15:11,696 --> 00:15:12,855
You need to realize

306
00:15:13,255 --> 00:15:15,976
I've grown close
with Deep In The Bustle recently.

307
00:15:16,375 --> 00:15:18,696
Mr. Tu is inviting me for tea tonight.

308
00:15:19,655 --> 00:15:20,615
So,

309
00:15:21,456 --> 00:15:22,735
find a scapegoat.

310
00:15:22,936 --> 00:15:23,615
Tomorrow,

311
00:15:23,775 --> 00:15:24,895
I want to see the result.

312
00:15:26,144 --> 00:15:26,720
Yes.

313
00:15:33,760 --> 00:15:37,523
♪If the heart can't hear the sorrow♪

314
00:15:37,783 --> 00:15:41,056
♪It only makes everything look so fake♪

315
00:15:42,666 --> 00:15:46,524
♪Your eyes resemble hers too much♪

316
00:15:46,976 --> 00:15:49,789
♪Who makes me forget whom♪

317
00:15:51,388 --> 00:15:55,029
♪The warmth in my heart is fading♪

318
00:15:55,215 --> 00:15:58,852
♪Every glance feels like atonement♪

319
00:16:00,192 --> 00:16:03,909
♪Ambiguity hidden in the night breeze♪

320
00:16:04,480 --> 00:16:09,536
♪Blows away the chance to explain♪

321
00:16:10,432 --> 00:16:13,984
♪I feel guilty♪

322
00:16:14,976 --> 00:16:18,528
♪I'll have no regrets
even I leave quietly♪

323
00:16:19,830 --> 00:16:22,987
♪Even in tears♪

324
00:16:23,840 --> 00:16:27,687
♪It doesn't matter♪

325
00:16:27,840 --> 00:16:31,563
♪We embrace in dreams♪

326
00:16:32,492 --> 00:16:35,958
♪I let down all my defenses♪

327
00:16:37,248 --> 00:16:40,498
♪Though the story has its end♪

328
00:16:41,344 --> 00:16:49,600
♪I'll journey with you all my life♪
